{"tid":50176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8架年初六啟市美食車部份營運點人流疏恐生意淡","createTime":"2016-12-22T08:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T11:33:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d63adec9fd62e8242b1cc001ecd447eaab05a69b","tid":50176,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:38:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161222/19873395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161222%2F19873395&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=34085ab7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161222%2F19873395&h=a626ba16\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161222/19873395</a><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本稱年底營業的美食車先導計劃，終落實明年2月2日（年初六）啟市，一半共8架美食車先營運，其餘陸續開業。不過《蘋果》了解過部份營運點，租金較貴的迪士尼樂園選址遠離大部份遊人途經地帶，亦有地點如黃大仙廣場鄰近施工中地盤，部份則食肆林立競爭極大。有美食車營運者周五將向當局要求提早於過年前試業。<br />\n記者：袁楚雙<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長蘇錦樑指，8架美食車可於明年年初六營業，目前只待領牌及與營運地點簽約後啟市，其餘8架車同月陸續開業。大部份經營者未取得牌照，據悉或可趕及首批啟業的美食車包括售鮮忌廉菠蘿包的天誠冰室、售美色叉包的大西洋未來食品等。天誠冰室老闆林啟忠希望可提早在過年前試業，周五將偕部份經營者與政府磋商。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161222/large/a0701a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161222%2Flarge%2Fa0701a.gif&h=3f6400e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n迪士尼選址在停車場<br />\n<br />\n本報上周五與法菜主廚伍永德觀察部份選址，包括月租第二貴、每月逾2.1萬元的迪士尼樂園選址。大部份人到迪士尼選乘港鐵、巴士或的士，但美食車選址不在乘客走往迪士尼途經方向，卻於相反方向，即近旅遊巴停車場位置，只有旅巴旅客或途經美食車。不過，就算巴士或港鐵乘客有意一嚐美食，也要走約200米路才找到美食車。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu0NP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu0NP.gif&h=923d1a57&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cu0NP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcu0NP.gif&h=923d1a57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2df9f8d666c7c99af966941ff0765cd1d36abe3","tid":50176,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161222/large/22la6p10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161222%2Flarge%2F22la6p10.jpg&h=739756ae&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n藝人谷祖琳設計的雞蛋仔入圍美食車先導計劃 <br />\n<br />\n記者停留半小時，發現該處主要是內地遊客經過，但半小時僅約70人，他指旅行團一般出發前在酒店吃早餐，園內又有餐飲，進園或離開時都未必停下吃東西。本地客則多用公共交通工具，認為美食車生意「會幾慘烈」。帶小朋友到迪士尼的李小姐指美食車地點偏遠，「樂園出口行到港鐵站都遠，仲要再行過去？」她認為若泊在噴水池附近較便利遊人。 <br />\n<br />\n觀塘天橋底午膳較旺 <br />\n<br />\n記者與伍再到觀塘海濱旁的起動九龍東（一號場），選址其實是天橋底，午膳較多打工仔途經，但其他時間明顯冷清。伍認為餐車至少可做到午膳人潮，惟區內食肆雲集，特色主題餐廳多，美食車面對的競爭非常大。 <br />\n<br />\n黃大仙廟旁邊正在擴建的黃大仙廣場選址是不少經營者的理想地，可吸引市民及旅客。但美食車泊位現仍為擴建工程地盤，車輛應需待工程完成後才可進駐，未知可否趕及新春期間營業。記者再到海洋公園選址，該處面向巴士總站，人潮如湧，但伍指樂園內餐飲眾多，是美食車面對的最大挑戰。美食車租金各有不同，但經營者需要輪流進駐，故每次都要重新計算成本，若賣較平價食物的進駐貴租時便較頭痛。 <br />\n<br />\n商經局回覆，考慮到營運場地要有足夠空間停車及排隊、容易到達、與現有食肆有一定距離等因素，才選定8個營運點，迪士尼停泊位與樂園港鐵站等交通設施只隔咫尺之距有優勢，屆時亦會設置指示牌。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i46zb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi46zb.gif&h=d6e78180&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i46zb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi46zb.gif&h=d6e78180&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db0f0fdf0fa5b25011e937d47e23ccac412dcd1b","tid":50176,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QbrT3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQbrT3.gif&h=1027dbae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36c686b06e94746dc5df265a1303cd9304fc3a8d","tid":50176,"uid":10442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"其實呢，食野好撚簡單<br />\n唔貴，份量夠，唔難食，就得架啦<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁撚多野"},{"pid":"97282b02a3bd39cea5678339771267d0f80badf0","tid":50176,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:17:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實呢，食野好撚簡單<br />\n唔貴，份量夠，唔難食，就得架啦<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁撚多野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搞咁撚多野只為將所有事物控制：<br />\n茶餐廳電視機只能播TVB<br />\n街頭小食只能幫襯美食車<br />\n外出時只能搭地下鐵路<br />\n平民一手樓上車只能買棺材房"},{"pid":"1ef0e7aea3cc4ca3589964815127ec965c56906a","tid":50176,"uid":33061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"真係人唔笑狗都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b77d24699365263918e7ec49a86aa5d8c5f3af","tid":50176,"uid":5603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:21:02.000Z","msg":"又係把撚雞蛋仔隊落個雪糕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387dc45177d1137b3e6213b18e0b411f4dfa5d3e","tid":50176,"uid":1152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:25:48.000Z","msg":"人戈"},{"pid":"cb7aad3f3449f9716b0c2d38c27ae17f62a4caf7","tid":50176,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"要比賽入圍仲好意思話自己係香港美食。<br />\n車仔檔邊有咁好心情比賽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90b1b99fd29041cf2be9cc4e3633a32d2fd8d84","tid":50176,"uid":1152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇蝕到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d87b702c99d3b2205776b76b6260838a833994","tid":50176,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685d1f319129d11f528a8fa42cfc88734ee7b92c","tid":50176,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:33:35.000Z","msg":"本都翻唔到"},{"pid":"ba08dbf6d7294484a554dc403b67052ed3068be7","tid":50176,"uid":35308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"痴Q線,市民係要嘅係桂林街果D小販車"}]}